  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/6b0cb73509373b991d6ec890cff1fe54.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=102 /></span><br><br>Elephant's Graveyard: A short but sweet, arcade horror game. Where you indirectly control Pinkston the pink elephant through a graveyard, with the help of a local crow named Leila.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/6322844213b91fc3228c21410bd02a4e.poster.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/6322844213b91fc3228c21410bd02a4e.webm?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/6322844213b91fc3228c21410bd02a4e.mp4?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use apples to lure Pinkston, guiding him carefully between breakable objects, like urns and tombs. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/c8993f5686d5feaa1160b5bcbb4e175c.poster.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/c8993f5686d5feaa1160b5bcbb4e175c.webm?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/c8993f5686d5feaa1160b5bcbb4e175c.mp4?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Disturbed from their eternal sleep, the undead inhabitants don't take kindly to Pinkston. Use different tactics to save Pinkston from their clutches.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/a924654f0cbe06cd58f3207491b03782.poster.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/a924654f0cbe06cd58f3207491b03782.webm?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/a924654f0cbe06cd58f3207491b03782.mp4?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Do not break too many urns! It will alert the Engineer, who will chase Pinkston down and drag him out of the level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/44fbc55c50e8f4a6877eabcdfc956886.poster.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/44fbc55c50e8f4a6877eabcdfc956886.webm?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/44fbc55c50e8f4a6877eabcdfc956886.mp4?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To unlock the gate to the next level, Pinkston needs to find keymice hiding between the urns.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pink elephant<br></li><li>4 levels to complete<br></li><li>Screen-filling boss battle<br></li><li>3 trophies to score each level<br></li><li>2 different endings<br></li><li>Lots of stuff to break<br></li><li>Banging soundtrack by Clement Panchout</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/6b0cb73509373b991d6ec890cff1fe54.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=102 /></span><br><br>Elephant's Graveyard: A short but sweet, arcade horror game. Where you indirectly control Pinkston the pink elephant through a graveyard, with the help of a local crow named Leila.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/6322844213b91fc3228c21410bd02a4e.poster.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/6322844213b91fc3228c21410bd02a4e.webm?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/6322844213b91fc3228c21410bd02a4e.mp4?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use apples to lure Pinkston, guiding him carefully between breakable objects, like urns and tombs. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/c8993f5686d5feaa1160b5bcbb4e175c.poster.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/c8993f5686d5feaa1160b5bcbb4e175c.webm?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/c8993f5686d5feaa1160b5bcbb4e175c.mp4?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Disturbed from their eternal sleep, the undead inhabitants don't take kindly to Pinkston. Use different tactics to save Pinkston from their clutches.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/a924654f0cbe06cd58f3207491b03782.poster.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/a924654f0cbe06cd58f3207491b03782.webm?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/a924654f0cbe06cd58f3207491b03782.mp4?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Do not break too many urns! It will alert the Engineer, who will chase Pinkston down and drag him out of the level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/44fbc55c50e8f4a6877eabcdfc956886.poster.avif?t=1652861449\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/44fbc55c50e8f4a6877eabcdfc956886.webm?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896930/extras/44fbc55c50e8f4a6877eabcdfc956886.mp4?t=1652861449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To unlock the gate to the next level, Pinkston needs to find keymice hiding between the urns.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pink elephant<br></li><li>4 levels to complete<br></li><li>Screen-filling boss battle<br></li><li>3 trophies to score each level<br></li><li>2 different endings<br></li><li>Lots of stuff to break<br></li><li>Banging soundtrack by Clement Panchout</li></ul>",
